This is an wishlist of features to add in future releases, in no
particular order:

* Documentation (format??)
* Fix all FIXMEs
* Debug and/or Verbose mode
* l10n ??
* mirror:// support in src_fetch()
* flag-o-matic functions
* Additional cygclasses:
	- docbook
	- git
	- kde3-split
	- xfce

* Whenever gstreamer starts new branch:
	mv gst-plugins.cygclass gst-plugins0.10.cygclass
	New gst-plugins.cygclass wrapper:
		inherit gst-plugins${PVP[0]}.$((PVP[1] + PVP[1] % 2))
    i.e. both 0.11.x and 0.12.x should use gst-plugins0.12
